          <p>The Biographical/Miscellaneous series is noteworthy for photographs of Steinberg's work in the 1940s with a strike of retail workers in New York. The images are of women workers voting to go out on strike. There are also images of Teamster presidents Dave Beck and James Hoffa at various union functions.</p>
